<emphasis bold="true" box="[1178,1199,1926,1952]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">C</emphasis>
. Antennal scape and flagellum. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[365,386,1961,1987]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">D</emphasis>
. Fore leg. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[513,533,1961,1987]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">E</emphasis>
. Mid leg. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[654,672,1961,1987]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">F</emphasis>
. Hind leg. 
